  "title": "Lab Technician - Science MNC / West #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Duration: Till End December 2026<br />Location: Tuas <br />Working Hours: Monday – Friday, 8:00am – 5:15pm<br />Salary: $2,000<br /><br /><strong> Job Scope: </strong></p><ul><li>- Assemble Single-Use Bio-Processing Containers for sterile liquid-handling in the biopharmaceutical industry</li><li>- Work in a Class 7 Cleanroom environment</li><li>- Follow standard work instructions and interpret technical drawings to ensure product quality</li><li>- Adhere strictly to ISO 13485:2016, ISO 22301:2019, and cGMP documentation standards</li><li>- Complete required training before performing tasks</li><li>- Ensure timely and accurate completion of batch records following Good Documentation Practice (GDP)</li><li>- Participate in Practical Process Improvement (PPI) initiatives</li><li>- Follow all safety protocols and cleanroom guidelines</li><li>- Work closely with engineers, QA, and maintenance teams</li><li>- Ensure proper storage and handling of materials to prevent contamination or damage</li><li>- Perform any other duties assigned by the Manager</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min. Nitec/ Diploma in any field </li><li>Able to commit till end Dec 2026 </li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
